name: Mr. Sambal - A Friend I Don't Have 07
description: The serious and mild manner appearance of Mr. Sambal may be misleading as he's infamous for his explosive temper. He's a social creature who likes to hang out with the likes of Mr. Bakso and Mr. Batagor, and Ms. PemPek but doesn't get along with Ms. Cendol. From "Friends I Don't Have" series.
